00:07:51,929 --> 00:07:52,930
Kenapa?

74
00:07:53,431 --> 00:07:57,268
Wajah Tuanku kemerahan.
Nampaknya, Tuanku demam.

75
00:07:58,311 --> 00:07:59,770
Tidak.

76
00:07:59,854 --> 00:08:02,273
Setelah seharian di luar,

77
00:08:03,065 --> 00:08:04,692
badan beta rasa hangat.

78
00:08:12,325 --> 00:08:13,326
Itu…

79
00:08:14,577 --> 00:08:18,873
Ia perlu dipulangkan semula
kepada tuannya esok pagi.

80
00:08:19,957 --> 00:08:21,417
Simpan dengan baik.

81
00:08:21,501 --> 00:08:22,335
Tuanku?

82
00:08:27,548 --> 00:08:31,093
Menjunjung perintah, Tuanku.

83
00:09:39,829 --> 00:09:43,374
Apa yang membuatkan Tuanku
leka ketika menunggang kuda

84
00:09:44,166 --> 00:09:46,502
