85
00:09:48,045 --> 00:09:49,922
Maafkan kita.

86
00:09:51,424 --> 00:09:54,385
Kebelakangan ini,
perilaku Tuanku kelihatan aneh.

87
00:10:05,563 --> 00:10:08,983
Tuanku cucu patik yang amat berharga.

88
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:12,570
Sebab itulah Tuanku
tak boleh miliki cacat cela.

89
00:10:13,070 --> 00:10:14,155
Tuanku faham?

90
00:10:15,865 --> 00:10:17,617
Faham, datuk.

91
00:10:55,905 --> 00:10:59,575
Maafkan kita.
Anakanda masih kekok menunggang kuda.

92
00:11:00,534 --> 00:11:01,619
Bonda tahu.

93
00:11:01,702 --> 00:11:04,622
Tentu anakanda lebih gementar
di depan datuk kamu.

94
00:11:06,248 --> 00:11:09,043
Bonda akan minta
Hulubalang Yoon untuk bantu kamu.

95
00:11:09,126 --> 00:11:11,712
Walaupun tak setanding
mendiang abang kamu,

96
00:11:12,254 --> 00:11:16,008
tapi pastikan tiada siapa
dapat bezakan kamu berdua.

97
00:11:17,468 --> 00:11:19,011
Baiklah, Tuanku.

98
00:11:19,095 --> 00:11:20,429
Usah panggil begitu.

99
00:11:25,351 --> 00:11:26,977
Luka kamu dalam.

100
00:11:27,061 --> 00:11:29,105
Pergi tukar pakaian kamu.

101
